desc: Sugar Fix Creations Adelaide Cakes and Desserts. Specialising in cakes, desserts and cookies for everyone and anyone. Cakes for any occasion, wedding cake, birthday cake, engagement cake, baptism cake or anniversary cake. Made to order cakes, party cakes, brownies, custom biscuits and delicious treats.

layout.text: Indulge in our amazing desserts and treats today!
Sugar Fix creates all sorts of amazing desserts including cupcakes, macarons, biscuits and cakes for all occasions or to eat whenever you want that sugar fix.
